@chapter Introduction to LightBot

LightBot is a Discord bot, that allows you to manage suggestions from your members in your server. 
There are a lots of features that does all the hard work behind the scenes for you.

@section Features

LightBot has the following features:

@itemize @bullet
@item Suggestion creation based on a suggestion channel, or a manual command
@item Restrict who can create suggestions
@item Delete suggestions
@item View suggestion meta
@item Change suggestion status (Notify user or Silent)
@item A few additional fun commands
@end itemize

